name: Hughes John
description:
I’m a fun lady who is building her life after some past hard time. I’m educated, currently building my business background and doing better. I’m open to learning something with the right man. I’m an open, outgoing, affectionate, articulate, and fun-loving person looking for the same in a partner. I’m a happy person who’s content with her life.
If you are caring, loving, and ready to meet a good listener and a fast learning woman. From being able to hold a great conversation to being open enough to express your needs and feelings. I’m super energetic, per ce, i am easy going reliable, sporting with a great sense of humor. I like to fish, yoga, sport, restaurant, swimming, cooking, pets.
